title: Amon Duul II - 11 Albums
description:
When asked to offer up a tune that perfectly illustrates "Teutonic Rock" I immediately cue up "Deutsch Nepal" from the Wolf City album..."Any questions?".  Considered by many to be the German Jefferson Airplane Amon Duul II are definitely up there with Guru Guru, Can, Grobschnitt, etal at the top of the cream of the crop of "Deutscher Psychedelic Exporten".  Highly recommended to anyone interested in Kraut Rock.

Here are the albums:

Carnival in Babylon
Hijack
Kobe (Reconsrtuctions)
Lemmingmania
Live in London
Live in Tokyo
Nada Moonshine
Pyragony X
Tanz der Lemminge [2002 Reissue]
Vive la Trance [Bonus Track]
Wolf City

Enjoy and please seed!;-}

Junco
